Red goes a long way, making it easy to add a few key accessories to create an overall holiday feel. It’s the only space in my home that features red this year!

As we head into the last few days before Christmas, I am cozying up to celebrate the magic of home with our new Johnelle Rectangle Cocktail Table and accessories from @ashleyofficialca! The table is oversized, beautiful, and features a planked top, in a weather grey finish. It’s the perfect addition to the space for movie nights!

One of my favourite ways to style for Christmas is by layering in holiday greenery and botanicals along side the decor. It’s simple, and impactful!

Head over to my stories for a closer look and direct links! The table is currently 30% off!

Our beautiful client came in today to get a Deep Cleansing Facial with our amazing Aesthetician, Manuela. 

An ice mask was applied to the face to cool and hydrate the skin. Then, red and blue LED light therapy was used to help with collagen production, soften fine lines and wrinkles, rejuvenate the skin, reduce inflammation and redness, and kill bacteria. 

To top it off, a décolleté massage was performed during this service for the ultimate experience.
